<%
  var pageTitle   = 'About — Lizzyland';
  var pageDesc    = 'Lizzyland exists for one reason — to help you live more beautifully.';
  var currentPage = 'about';
%>
<%- include('partials/header') %>

<style>
  /* ── About hero — warm dark, no image ── */
  .ll-about-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--warm-dark) 0%, #3d2510 60%, var(--warm-mid) 100%);
    min-height: 280px;
    display: flex; align-items: flex-end;
    padding: 0;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ll-about-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 15% 60%, rgba(200,149,42,0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 30%, rgba(26,138,122,0.07) 0%, transparent 40%);
  }
  .ll-about-hero-inner {
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%; padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
  }
  .ll-about-hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em; opacity: 0.8; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .ll-about-hero-inner h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
    color: var(--white); margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
  }
  .ll-about-hero-inner p {
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Main philosophy section ── */
  .ll-about-philosophy {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: var(--sand-light);
  }
  .ll-about-philosophy-inner {
    max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .ll-about-ornament {
    font-size: 1rem; color: var(--gold); opacity: 0.6;
    letter-spacing: 0.5rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .ll-about-philosophy h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--warm-dark); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .ll-about-philosophy-lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--text-soft);
    line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .ll-about-philosophy-lead em {
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic;
    color: var(--warm-dark); font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  /* ── Profile block ── */
  .ll-about-guide {
    padding: 0 2rem 5rem;
    background: var(--sand-light);
  }
  .ll-about-guide-inner {
    max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex; align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem; padding: 3rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--sand-deep);
  }
  .ll-about-guide-portrait {
    width: 160px; height: 160px;
    border-radius: 50%; overflow: hidden;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border: 3px solid var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(200,149,42,0.2);
  }
  .ll-about-guide-portrait img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
  }
  .ll-about-guide-text { flex: 1; }
  .ll-about-guide-role {
    font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .ll-about-guide-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--warm-dark); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .ll-about-guide-bio {
    font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-soft);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .ll-about-contact {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.55rem 1.4rem;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--ocean);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    color: var(--ocean); font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.85rem; transition: all 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .ll-about-contact:hover { background: var(--ocean); color: var(--white); }

  /* ── Dolce Vita principles ── */
  .ll-about-principles {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--warm-dark) 0%, #3d2510 100%);
  }
  .ll-about-principles-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .ll-about-principles h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--white); text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .ll-about-principles-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic;
    text-align: center; color: rgba(245,230,200,0.55);
    font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .ll-principles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .ll-principle-card {
    background: rgba(245,230,200,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,230,200,0.12);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }
  .ll-principle-card:hover {
    background: rgba(245,230,200,0.1);
    border-color: rgba(200,149,42,0.4);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
  .ll-principle-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold-light); margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .ll-principle-desc {
    font-size: 0.88rem; color: rgba(245,230,200,0.6);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ── Closing quote ── */
  .ll-about-closing {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: var(--sand-light);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .ll-about-closing-inner { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .ll-about-closing-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-accent); font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.7rem);
    color: var(--warm-dark); line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .ll-about-doors-prompt {
    font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .ll-about-doors-links { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .ll-about-door-btn {
    display: inline-block; padding: 0.65rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl); font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.88rem; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .ll-about-door-btn.health { background: var(--ocean-pale); color: var(--ocean); border: 1.5px solid var(--ocean); }
  .ll-about-door-btn.health:hover { background: var(--ocean); color: var(--white); }
  .ll-about-door-btn.wealth { background: #fdf3e3; color: var(--gold); border: 1.5px solid var(--gold); }
  .ll-about-door-btn.wealth:hover { background: var(--gold); color: var(--white); }
  .ll-about-door-btn.happy { background: var(--ocean-pale); color: var(--ocean); border: 1.5px solid var(--ocean); }
  .ll-about-door-btn.happy:hover { background: var(--ocean); color: var(--white); }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .ll-about-guide-inner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .ll-principles-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }
  }
</style>

  <!-- ══ HERO ══ -->
  <section class="ll-about-hero">
    <div class="ll-about-hero-inner">
      <div class="ll-about-hero-eyebrow">✦ The Philosophy ✦</div>
      <h1>About Lizzyland</h1>
      <p>A guide to the good life — curated, intentional, entirely yours.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ PHILOSOPHY ══ -->
  <section class="ll-about-philosophy">
    <div class="ll-about-philosophy-inner">
      <span class="ll-about-ornament">✦ · ✦ · ✦</span>
      <h2>Lizzyland exists for one reason.</h2>
      <p class="ll-about-philosophy-lead">
        To help you live more beautifully.<br><br>
        Not perfectly. Not productively. <em>Beautifully.</em><br><br>
        La dolce vita — the sweet life — is not a holiday mindset. It is a way of being.
        It is the art of savouring what is in front of you, moving through the world
        with intention, and choosing quality of life over the relentless pursuit of more.
        <br><br>
        Your life is a blessing. Be a blessing.
        Everything here is designed to help you remember that.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ THE GUIDE ══ -->
  <section class="ll-about-guide">
    <div class="ll-about-guide-inner">
      <div class="ll-about-guide-portrait">
        <img src="/images/lizzy-profile-lizzyland.jpg" alt="Lizzy" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
      </div>
      <div class="ll-about-guide-text">
        <div class="ll-about-guide-role">Your Guide</div>
        <div class="ll-about-guide-name">Lizzy</div>
        <p class="ll-about-guide-bio">
          Life coach, web architect, and benevolent curator of the good life.
          I help people find their way to what they actually want —
          not what they think they want.
          I build beautiful digital spaces, curate extraordinary experiences,
          and gently point people toward their beautiful future.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@lizzyland.xyz" class="ll-about-contact">
          hello@lizzyland.xyz
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ LA DOLCE VITA PRINCIPLES ══ -->
  <section class="ll-about-principles">
    <div class="ll-about-principles-inner">
      <h2>La Dolce Vita</h2>
      <p class="ll-about-principles-sub">The principles that guide everything here.</p>
      <div class="ll-principles-grid">
        <div class="ll-principle-card">
          <div class="ll-principle-title">Savour Everything</div>
          <p class="ll-principle-desc">Linger over meals. Enjoy your coffee slowly. Value what is fresh, seasonal and made with care. Eating is not fuel — it is pleasure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ll-principle-card">
          <div class="ll-principle-title">Slow Down</div>
          <p class="ll-principle-desc">Reject the constant rush. Favour a more present, leisurely pace. The best moments in life cannot be rushed — they can only be received.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ll-principle-card">
          <div class="ll-principle-title">Cultivate Connection</div>
          <p class="ll-principle-desc">Spend time with people you love. Socialise without agenda. The quality of your relationships determines the quality of your life.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ll-principle-card">
          <div class="ll-principle-title">Dress with Intention</div>
          <p class="ll-principle-desc">Style is not vanity — it is self-respect. Dressing well is a way of showing joy, confidence, and care for the life you are living.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ll-principle-card">
          <div class="ll-principle-title">Find Beauty Daily</div>
          <p class="ll-principle-desc">Appreciate art, history, and the beauty of your surroundings. Joy is not a destination — it is a daily practice of noticing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ll-principle-card">
          <div class="ll-principle-title">Rest Without Guilt</div>
          <p class="ll-principle-desc">Do not apologise for taking breaks, enjoying long lunches, or taking vacations. Rest is not laziness — it is the source of everything good.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ CLOSING ══ -->
  <section class="ll-about-closing">
    <div class="ll-about-closing-inner">
      <div class="ll-about-closing-quote">
        "Your life is a blessing.<br>Be a blessing.<br>And live it beautifully."
      </div>
      <p class="ll-about-doors-prompt">Choose your door.</p>
      <div class="ll-about-doors-links">
        <a href="/health" class="ll-about-door-btn health">Health</a>
        <a href="/space"  class="ll-about-door-btn wealth">Wealth</a>
        <a href="/shop"   class="ll-about-door-btn happy">Happiness</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="ll-divider">✦ · ✦ · ✦</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
